IN RE SOUTHEASTERN EYE CENTER-PENDING MATTERS In re Southeastern Eye Center-Judgments No. 168A17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018

ORDER

Appellant has failed to demonstrate grounds for appellate review under N.C.G.S. 7A-27(a)(3) (2017). The appeal in this matter is therefore dismissed.

By order of the Court in Conference, this the 1 st day of March, 2018.
